{"title":"盆栽的仙人球","authors":["洪迪"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":12,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"盆栽的仙人球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浙江台州地区　洪迪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是被幽禁的古代武士？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失去了用武之地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空挺着带刺的青剑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管这儿有富裕的水和养料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你仍然向往沙漠的贫瘠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙漠雄豪的空旷和灼热的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片雄心，一身本领，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能消磨在紫沙抟成的囹圄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一截朝暮锈烂的废铁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，悄悄地铸你绿色的剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓦然，你勇猛地刺向星天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满怀壮志绽开剑尖的美艳！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}